LabDelivery

agents
	Nurse
	LabPersonnel
	Transporter
	Arm
locations
	patientFloor
	laboratory
resources
	sample

Nurse:
	1: fetch sample
	2: stop

LabPersonnel:
	1: stop

Transporter:
	1: moveTo patientFloor
	2: receiveFrom Nurse
	3: moveTo laboratory
	4: stop

Arm:
	1-3: stop
	4: receiveFrom Transporter
	5: deliver sample

success: !possess(Transporter, sample)
failure: time(20)